data.description: Multiple offers. Lowest priced Forest Lakes single family home. This 3 bedroom+den home is centrally located in the heart of Naples in an outstanding school district just 2.5 miles from the best Naples beaches. No HOA fees in this highly sought after community.  It is walking distance to the Quail Run Golf Club where a limited number of Preview Memberships are available.  This fenced corner lot location and appealing structure are a valuable combination! The 3 bedroom plus 270 square foot den/flex/FL room home has a full 505 square foot two car garage.  Kitchen has a breakfast bar, pass through window, pantry, and a double sink. Roof was replaced in 2018. 5 lighted ceiling fans. Floors are tile except the bedrooms. Two bedrooms were newly carpeted in March. Ideal location close to beaches, Mercato, Venetian Village, Waterside Shops, medical facilities, hospitals and A+ schools. City utilities; assessments paid. Enjoy a wide variety of shops, world-class culture and a diversity of casual and fine dining restaurants including the best seafood in SW Florida. This is an affordable family destination in the center of Naples that appeals to nature lovers, golfers and beach enthusiasts.
